      • getSuperPlayerMaker

        public Player getSuperPlayerMaker(int teamId)
        This query finds the "Super Play Maker" player, a "Super Play Maker" player is the player that has the largest value, is a right leg kicker, is in MIDFIELDER position and is in a team's first players. if there are more than one player the method returns the first player
        Parameters:
        teamId - to get its SuperPlayerMaker
        Returns:
        player object if found, null otherwise
